<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.8.10">
<l>māṭa māḷikai cūḻtiru maṅkai maṉṉa ṉoṉṉalar taṅkaḷai vellum</l>
<l>āṭal māvala vaṉkali kaṉṟi yaṇipo ḻiltiru varaṅkat tammāṉai</l>
<l>nīṭu tolpuka ḻāḻival lāṉai yentai yaineṭu mālaini ṉainta</l>
<l>pāṭal pattivai pāṭumiṉ toṇṭīr pāṭa nummiṭaip pāvanil lāvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Devotees! Sing these ten songs of Kalikaṉṟi, king of prosperous Maṅkai,</l>
<l rend="indent">encircled by mansions and palaces,</l>
<l>The one skilled with fighting elephants who subdues his foes,</l>
<l>(These) which meditate on tall Māl, our father, the one skilled with the discus</l>
<l rend="indent">of long, ancient fame,</l>
<l>Lord of sacred Araṅkam with lovely groves; when you sing,</l>
<l rend="indent">sins will not remain near you.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
